data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 3/2 ranch-style gem with a bonus room is the epitome of comfort and style. As you approach, you'll be greeted by an inviting front entrance with a circular driveway and much curb appeal adding a touch of sophistication to your daily routine. The metal roof not only enhances curb appeal but also promises durability for years to come. Step inside, and you'll immediately feel the airy and welcoming ambiance that fills every corner of this home. The kitchen, featuring ample counter space, contemporary appliances, and a layout that effortlessly flows into the dining and living areas, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating unforgettable memories with loved ones. A highlight of this property is the recently updated plumbing system, and a brand new drainfield ensuring peace of mind and hassle-free living making this home truly move-in ready. For those who relish outdoor living, this home boasts a 6' fenced-in private yard that's perfect for enjoying warm summer evenings, hosting BBQs, or simply unwinding in your own oasis of tranquility. And when you're in the mood for fresh air without the bugs, the screened-in porch is an idyllic retreat. In summary, this home is an absolute must-see. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home. Schedule a showing today and let your dreams come true.
